Sentencas: Thick films of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 (LSM) were deposited on impervious YSZ electrolyte by the screen printing technique.
Titulo: Preparation of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 thick films as cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The LSM powders used in this investigation were synthesized by autoignition of carboxylate-nitrate gel.
Titulo: Preparation of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 thick films as cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Multiple coatings were applied to increase the thickness of LSM layer.
Titulo: Preparation of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 thick films as cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Effects of coating thickness and sintering temperature on the microstructure and electrical properties of the films were studied.
Titulo: Preparation of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 thick films as cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The properties of the films obtained from the present study, fulfill the requirements of the cathode of a solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Preparation of Sr-substituted LaMnO3 thick films as cathode for solid oxide fuel cell
